                My expertise lies in building data-intensive backend systems and mobile applications, with a strong focus on <code>.NET/C#</code> and scalable system architectures.
              </p>
              <p>
                From time to time I also like to post some videos on my ðŸ“º YouTube channel, where I share insights and tutorials about cross-platform tools and applications, such as AvaloniaUI.
